title: Spacious first floor 2 Bedroom + 3 season porch
posting_body: ['Ideal Walkable Location:', '- 2 blocks from Bde Maka Ska and the beach.', '- 1 block from the grocery store, coffee shops, restaurants, shopping, and more!', '- 3 blocks to the greenway', '- 10 minute drive to University of Minnesota', '- Uptown living with a quiet neighborhood feel.', 'Features include:', '- Free laundry', '- Classy hardwood floors and tiled bathroom', '- Beautiful shared backyard with gardening options for fresh vegetables and BBQ grill', '- Lots of windows and tall ceilings', '- Handcrafted wood detailing, original woodwork, and build in hutch', '- 3 season porch', '- New appliances', '- Dishwasher', '- Great neighborhood (East Bde Maka Ska) and engaged neighbors with parties and events', 'Specifics:', '-Owner occupant', '-Bedrooms: 2', '-Bathrooms: 1', '-Available: October 1, 2022', '-1400 sq. ft.', '-Min.', 'Lease: 11 months to 20 months', '-Parking:', 'Off street parking spots available', '-Deposit: one months rent', '-Laundry: Free on-site', '-Storage: Ample basement storage+ bike storage', '-Non', 'Smoking', '-Cat', 'Allowed with pet lease and pet rent, small dogs negotiable', '-Window AC units optional', '-Tenant pays: Gas-Heat/Electric', '-Trash, water, laundry, and maintenance included in rent.']
